                     <interp inst="t18310106-36-person401" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I am an officer. I was on duty on the evening of the 18th of December, and saw the prisoner running away; I followed him, and when I came up to him I said, "Come, young man, you must come back with me;" he said, "For God's sake, let me go - it is the first thing I ever did;" this is the mutton which he had; I found only one penny and one farthing on him.</p>
               <p>Prisoner. I have a wife and four children in the greatest distress.</p>
               <p>GUILTY. Aged 36.</p>
